OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome areas of cloud to start
OL,6,Fthe morning, mainly affecting parts of
OL,7,FNorfolk. This clearing then all areas
OL,8,Fsunny. Feeling hot or very hot by
OL,9,Fafternoon. Slightly cooler near some
OL,10,Fcoasts. Winds light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine night with mostly
OL,13,Fclear skies across the region. Some
OL,14,Flow cloud possible later in the night
OL,15,Facross some coasts. Winds remaining
OL,16,Flight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FA similar day to Wednesday
OL,19,Fwith plenty of sunshine and turning
OL,20,Fhot or very hot by afternoon. Winds
OL,21,Fremaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
