OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRemaining
OL,6,Flargely dry, sunny and hot throughout.
OL,7,FIsolated thundery showers possible
OL,8,Flater Friday and Saturday. A
OL,9,Ffreshening north-easterly wind
OL,10,Fdeveloping by Saturday. Temperatures
OL,11,Fwell above average.
